Package: istatlab
Type: Package
Title: Download and Process Italian Labour Market Data from ISTAT
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2026-02-11
Author: Giampaolo Montaletti [aut, cre] (0009-0002-5327-1122)
Maintainer: Giampaolo Montaletti <giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Giampaolo", "Montaletti", 
           email = "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5327-1122"))
Description: A toolkit for downloading and processing Italian labour market and
    demographic data from ISTAT (Istituto Nazionale di Statistica). Supports both
    the SDMX API (esploradati.istat.it) for labour market data and static CSV
    downloads (demo.istat.it) for demographic data including population, births,
    deaths, migrations, and projections. Provides functions for data retrieval,
    metadata handling, caching, and data processing with automatic label application.
